    5.0 out of 5 stars Works extremely well!!
    Reviewed in the United States on 22 October 2023
    Pattern Name: Fashion Tape Pack of 1Verified Purchase
    I bought this body tape for my wedding dress since it was made of a very heavy material and had an open back that could lead to the shoulders slipping off. I bought this tape hoping that it would keep my dress from moving and IT DID!! I would highly recommend this. My dress did not move all night and I danced and jumped and partied. The best way to get the tape to be effective is place it on your body and then let it sit for a minute or two before moving. This allows the adhesive to set up.
